\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTemplateElement\"><code>HTMLTemplateElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTextAreaElement\"><code>HTMLTextAreaElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/HTMLTimeElement\"><code>HTMLTimeElement</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTitleElement\"><code>HTMLTitleElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTrackElement\"><code>HTMLTrackElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLUListElement\"><code>HTMLUListElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/HTMLUnknownElement\"><code>HTMLUnknownElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/HTMLVideoElement\"><code>HTMLVideoElement</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HashChangeEvent\"><code>HashChangeEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/History\"><code>History</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/ImageData\"><code>ImageData</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/Location\"><code>Location</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MessageChannel\"><code>MessageChannel</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/MessageEvent\"><code>MessageEvent</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MessagePort\"><code>MessagePort</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/Navigator\"><code>Navigator</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/PageTransitionEvent\"><code>PageTransitionEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/Plugin\"><code>Plugin</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PluginArray\"><code>PluginArray</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PopStateEvent\"><code>PopStateEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PromiseRejectionEvent\"><code>PromiseRejectionEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RadioNodeList\"><code>RadioNodeList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ValidityState\"><code>ValidityState</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p>La mixin <strong><code>WindowEventHandlers</code></strong> décrit les gestionnaires d'événements communs à plusieurs interfaces comme <a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a>, or <a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/HTMLBodyElement\"><code>HTMLBodyElement</code></a> et <a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/HTMLFrameSetElement\"><code>HTMLFrameSetElement</code></a>. Chacune de ces interfaces peut implémenter des gestionnaires d'événement supplémentaires.<p></p>\n<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p><strong>Note :</strong> <code>WindowEventHandlers</code> est une mixin et non une interface; il n'est pas possible de créer un objet de type <code>WindowEventHandlers</code>.</p>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"propriétés","title":"Propriétés","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>Les propriétés d'événement, de la forme <code>onXYZ</code>, sont définis sur <a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/WindowEventHandlers\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>WindowEventHandlers</code></a> et implémentées par <a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a> ou <a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a> pour les Web Workers.</em></p>\n<dl>\n  <dt id=\"windoweventhandlers.onafterprint\"><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/Window/afterprint_event\"><code>WindowEventHandlers.onafterprint</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Est un <code><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/Reference/Events/Event_handlers\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">event handler</a></code> représentant le code à appeler lorsque l'événement <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/afterprint_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">afterprint (en-US)</a></code> est déclenché.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"windoweventhandlers.onbeforeprint\"><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/Window/beforeprint_event\"><code>WindowEventHandlers.onbeforeprint</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Est un <code><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/Reference/Events/Event_handlers\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">event handler</a></code> représentant le code à appeler lorsque l'événement <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/beforeprint_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">beforeprint (en-US)</a></code> est déclenché.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"windoweventhandlers.onbeforeunload\"><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/Window/beforeunload_event\"><code>WindowEventHandlers.onbeforeunload</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Est un <code><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/Reference/Events/Event_handlers\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">event handler</a></code> représentant le code à appeler lorsque l'événement <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/beforeunload_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">beforeunload (en-US)</a></code> est déclenché.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"windoweventhandlers.onhashchange\"><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/Window/hashchange_event\"><code>WindowEventHandlers.onhashchange</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Est un <code><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/Reference/Events/Event_handlers\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">event handler</a></code> représentant le code à appeler lorsque l'événement <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/hashchange_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">hashchange (en-US)</a></code> est déclenché.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"windoweventhandlers.onlanguagechange\"><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/Window/languagechange_event\"><code>WindowEventHandlers.onlanguagechange</code></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Est un <code><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/Reference/Events/Event_handlers\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">event handler</a></code> représentant le code à appeler lorsque l'événement <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/languagechange_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">languagechange (en-US)</a></code> est déclenché.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"windoweventhandlers.onmessage_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/message_event\"><code>WindowEventHandlers.onmessage</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Est un <code><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/Reference/Events/Event_handlers\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">event handler</a></code> représentant le code à appeler lorsque l'événement <code><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/Reference/Events/message\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">message</a></code> est déclenché.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"windoweventhandlers.onoffline\"><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"Cette documentation n'a pas encore été rédigée, vous pouvez aider en contribuant&nbsp;!\"><code>WindowEventHandlers.onoffline</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Est un <code><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/Reference/Events/Event_handlers\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">event handler</a></code> représentant le code à appeler lorsque l'événement <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/offline_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">offline (en-US)</a></code> est déclenché.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"windoweventhandlers.ononline\"><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"Cette documentation n'a pas encore été rédigée, vous pouvez aider en contribuant&nbsp;!\"><code>WindowEventHandlers.ononline</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Est un <code><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/Reference/Events/Event_handlers\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">event handler</a></code> représentant le code à appeler lorsque l'événement <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/online_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">online (en-US)</a></code> est déclenché.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"windoweventhandlers.onpagehide\"><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"Cette documentation n'a pas encore été rédigée, vous pouvez aider en contribuant&nbsp;!\"><code>WindowEventHandlers.onpagehide</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Est un <code><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/Reference/Events/Event_handlers\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">event handler</a></code> représentant le code à appeler lorsque l'événement <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/pagehide_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">pagehide (en-US)</a></code> est déclenché.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"windoweventhandlers.onpageshow\"><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"Cette documentation n'a pas encore été rédigée, vous pouvez aider en contribuant&nbsp;!\"><code>WindowEventHandlers.onpageshow</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Est un <code><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/Reference/Events/Event_handlers\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">event handler</a></code> représentant le code à appeler lorsque l'événement <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/pageshow_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">pageshow (en-US)</a></code> est déclenché.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"windoweventhandlers.onpopstate\"><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/Window/popstate_event\"><code>WindowEventHandlers.onpopstate</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Est un <code><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/Reference/Events/Event_handlers\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">event handler</a></code> représentant le code à appeler lorsque l'événement <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/popstate_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">popstate (en-US)</a></code> est déclenché.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"windoweventhandlers.onresize\"><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"Cette documentation n'a pas encore été rédigée, vous pouvez aider en contribuant&nbsp;!\"><code>WindowEventHandlers.onresize</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Est un <code><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/Reference/Events/Event_handlers\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">event handler</a></code> représentant le code à appeler lorsque l'événement <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/resize_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">resize (en-US)</a></code> est déclenché.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"windoweventhandlers.onstorage_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/storage_event\"><code>WindowEventHandlers.onstorage</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Est un <code><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/Reference/Events/Event_handlers\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">event handler</a></code> représentant le code à appeler lorsque l'événement <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/storage_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">storage (en-US)</a></code> est déclenché.</p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"windoweventhandlers.onunload\"><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/Window/unload_event\"><code>WindowEventHandlers.onunload</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Est un <code><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/Reference/Events/Event_handlers\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">event handler</a></code> représentant le code à appeler lorsque l'événement <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/unload_event\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">unload (en-US)</a></code> est déclenché.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"méthodes","title":"Méthodes","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>Cette interface ne définit aucune méthode.</em></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spécifications","title":"Spécifications","isH3":false,"content":"<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Specification</th>\n      <th>Status</th>\n      <th>Comment</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/#windoweventhandlers\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"fr\">La définition de 'GlobalEventHandlers' dans cette spécification.</small></a></td>\n      <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Standard évolutif</span></td>\n      <td>Pas de changement depuis <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html51/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"La spécificaction 'HTML 5.1'\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML 5.1</a>.</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html51/#windoweventhandlers\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML 5.1<br><small lang=\"fr\">La définition de 'GlobalEventHandlers' dans cette spécification.</small></a></td>\n      <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n      <td>Snapshot de <a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"La spécificaction 'HTML Living Standard'\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard</a>. Ajoute <code>onlanguage</code>.</td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html52/#windoweventhandlers\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5<br><small lang=\"fr\">La définition de 'GlobalEventHandlers' dans cette spécification.</small></a></td>\n      <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n      <td>Snapshot de <a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" title=\"La spécificaction 'HTML Living Standard'\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard</a>. Création de <code>WindowEventHandlers</code> (les propriétés étaient sur la cible avant).</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Compatibilité des navigateurs","id":"compatibilité_des_navigateurs","isH3":false,"query":"api.WindowEventHandlers","dataURL":"/fr/docs/Web/API/WindowEventHandlers/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"voir_aussi","title":"Voir aussi","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a> et <a href=\"/fr/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Propriétés","id":"propriétés"},{"text":"Méthodes","id":"méthodes"},{"text":"Spécifications","id":"spécifications"},{"text":"Compatibilité des navigateurs","id":"compatibilité_des_navigateurs"},{"text":"Voir aussi","id":"voir_aussi"}],"summary":"Les propriétés d'événement, de la forme onXYZ, sont définis sur WindowEventHandlers et implémentées par Window ou WorkerGlobalScope pour les Web Workers.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"WindowEventHandlers","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"WindowEventHandlers","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"WindowEventHandlers","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"WindowEventHandlers","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"WindowEventHandlers","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"WindowEventHandlers","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"fr/web/api/windoweventhandlers","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/fr/web/api/windoweventhandlers/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/fr/docs/Web","title":"Technologies web pour développeurs"},{"uri":"/fr/docs/Web/API","title":"Référence Web API"},{"uri":"/fr/docs/Web/API/WindowEventHandlers","title":"WindowEventHandlers"}],"pageTitle":"WindowEventHandlers - Référence Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}